title: Jindal campaign raised less than $600,000 last quarter
text: Louisiana Gov. Bobby Jindal, who has struggled to break out of the bottom tier of 2016 GOP presidential candidates since launching his bid in June, raised less than $600,000 during the third fundraising quarter in 2015.
